00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:41,220
 John is placing the eternal word,

284
00:14:41,220 --> 00:14:44,480
 the eternal son of God, who would take on flesh

285
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:46,340
 in the person of Jesus Christ,

286
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:51,340
 he is placing him before the creation of the world.

287
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:56,540
 The eternal word that we now know as Jesus

288
00:14:56,540 --> 00:14:59,060
 is in fact God.

289
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:02,380
 He's not just a wise teacher.

290
00:15:02,380 --> 00:15:04,360
 He's not just a prophet.

291
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:07,260
 He's not just a significant religious figure.

292
00:15:07,260 --> 00:15:10,180
 He is God.

293
00:15:10,180 --> 00:15:12,940
 And to believe that he's just a good man

294
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:17,940
 or a wise teacher is crazy because Jesus claimed to be God

295
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:21,860
 and all of his followers claimed that he was God.

296
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:24,620
 So if someone is claiming to be God,

297
00:15:24,620 --> 00:15:29,620
 but he's just a man and not God,

298
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:33,620
 that either makes him a liar or a crazy person.

299
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:39,000
 And so the reality is Jesus is God.

300
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:42,520
 The God of Christianity is the God where Jesus is God.

301
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:45,620
 If Jesus isn't God, then it isn't Christianity.

302
00:15:45,620 --> 00:15:48,240
 Have you ever thought of Jesus being God?

303
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,080
 What about this?

304
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:52,600
 Have you ever thought of Jesus as the creator of all things?

305
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,440
 Look at what John says in verses two and three.

306
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:57,000
 He says, "He," referring to the word,

307
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,960
 who we now know as Jesus,

308
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,640
 "He was in the beginning with God.

309
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:02,980
 "All things," watch that,

310
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:05,700
 "All things were made through him.

311
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:09,840
 "And without him was not anything made that was made."

