00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:50,860
 It was actually to symbolize evil within humanity

360
00:18:50,860 --> 00:18:53,980
 in the absence of spiritual life.

361
00:18:53,980 --> 00:18:56,020
 So what John is saying when he says,

362
00:18:56,020 --> 00:18:57,700
 "The light shines in the darkness

363
00:18:57,700 --> 00:18:59,620
 "and the darkness has not overcome it,"

364
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:02,460
 is he is saying that not only is Jesus

365
00:19:02,460 --> 00:19:04,560
 the sustainer of physical life,

366
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:09,560
 but he is our only hope for spiritual life,

367
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:12,060
 life with God.

368
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:14,620
 So the reason that I tell you this,

